\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Generic Jastrow (ic)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This Jastrow factor implements a generic power series with 
\begin_inset Formula $U_{ij}^{ee}$
\end_inset

 as in Schmidt-Moskowitz and 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
U_{ai}^{en}=\sum_{m=1}^{m_{max}}c_{m}^{en}\bar{r}_{ai}^{m}
\]

\end_inset

(note the missing factor 
\begin_inset Formula $(n-1)$
\end_inset

 in comparison with Schmidt-Moskowitz).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The form of the een terms is described in the report on Jastrow factors.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
